subject: Jasta: Res
message:
Sweet Jasta,
We faeries have heard your prayer and will grant you a great boon if 
you undertake a path through the Dreamlands and into the very soul 
of the world.
A journey such as this is very dangerous, so in order to prepare, 
find a sight that when beheld your mind fills with thoughts of 
ancient priests and battles.  Arrive at this location with the 
following to begin the ritual to revive the dead.

As you seek the power to return life, seek out a life stolen that 
may be returned.  Bring with it the essence of life, the crimson 
beauty that sets the foretelling morning sky ablaze.  Study THRICE 
the forces of DEATH from differing parts of the land, and 
THRICE the will of the LIVING, so that you might get a glimpse at 
the miracle you wish to perform.  Study the THREE CORPSEs, never 
decaying, that you may see how to reverse the deaths and restore the 
bodies.  Bring with you one foci from each body.

With this knowledge, construct a circle using THREE each of the four 
elements.  Bring ROCKs to be the Earth, one of which must be used to 
complete a planar gate elsewhere in the realm.  LIGHTNING for Air, 
of which be sure to find a completed circle.  True WATER for Water, 
though one must be formidable enough to protect you from spirits that 
might try to revive themselves through your workings.  FIRE for Fire, 
at least one of which must be the true essence of the word.

To find the mystic power that fuels the glory of the Resurrection, 
you must look within the source of dreams, the Reverie.  Fill your 
mind with the transcendent aroma of SIX MUSHROOMs and NINE HERBs, 
burned in FOUR BOWLs.  Release their powers with SMOKING, SMOLDERING, 
and THREE BURNING objects.  Contemplate your three foci and they will 
draw you into the beautiful land of the Dreaming.  
Within the Reverie, you shall receive visions of walking CORPSEs 
numbering THREE, and haunted GHOSTs numbering THREE BY THREE.  Be 
warned, for visions here are as real and as dangerous as those 
experienced in the waking world!  Channel their powers into a DIAMOND 
worth at least 5000 GP, which shall forever be your connection to the 
world of the spirits.
~
~~
level: 101
poster: Daedela
time: 1181836800
subject: Saka: Res
message:
To the Prince of Dark Ways, Saka,The Unseelie courts have heard your plee and will grant your powerful 
request.  However, the power to resurrect the dead does not come 
cheaply.  A visit to the Reverie at the heart of the Dreamlands will 
be required to harness this miraculous spell. 

First, you will have to free a stolen soul to guide you.  He has long 
known the true horror of death.  Second, you must revive him with 
BLOOD, retrieved from a place of utter desecration.  You as well must 
experience first-hand the forces that you seek to command, so your 
guide may speak to you as a kindred.  Find THRICE DEATH, each in a 
different corner of the realms, and THRICE the strong will of the 
LIVING.  Once you have grappled with their powerful intents, you 
shall be ready to being your voyage into the heart of nightmares.

With this knowledge in your heart, construct a circle using THREE each 
of the four elements.  Bring ROCKs to be the Earth, one of which must 
be used to complete a planar gate elsewhere in the realm.  LIGHTNING 
for Air, of which be sure to find a completed circle.  True WATER for 
Water, though one must be formidable enough to protect you from 
spirits that might try to revive themselves through your workings.  
FIRE for Fire, at least one of which must be the true essence of the 
word.

In order to be granted your power, you must prove that you are 
dedicated to the forces of Chaos, for resurrection is nothing short of 
perverting the natural flow of life and death, throwing the heavens 
into tumultuous disarray!  Writing binds the world together in a 
coherent, provable fashion.  In such a method, the vast powers of the 
Fae are limited and restrained.  To unleash our true potential, 
recover NINE books and burn them in the ritual flames.  Bring with you 
SIX ETHEREAL forces to protect your very soul from being torn asunder, 
and then release the powers of THREE sources of CHAOS.  In doing so, 
you will be taken fully into the Reverie and shown a vision of your 
own great ancestors . THREE DEMON LORDS.
Perform to each Lord a sacrifice of THREE: SWIRLING sacrifices to one 
who watches the same, BLOOD sacrifices to one who drinks endlessly, 
and WAR sacrifices to one entrenched in an eternal battlefield.  As 
proof of your love, give to each a different corrupted, fallen or evil 
SYMBOL as well.  Once you have placated them, find the correct focus 
so that .You feel something within you mend, and a power from beyond 
merging with your own..  This will be the granting of their powers.  
Then, return to the waking world with either their memories or proof 
of your visit.

Finally, your focus for the casting of this spell must be a DIAMOND, 
worth no less than 5000 GP.  Be sure to bring such a thing with you 
before you enter into the Dreaming, or else your trip will be wasted 
and your power lost.


Daedela, Envoy of the Unseelie Court
~
~~
