and of two BLOODY carnage.  Circle these items around the ritual
flames, atop which you must envelop the corpses of eight MASTERs
of trade.  In these fires, destroy five RODs, five HOT items, and
one MAPLE.  With this complete, you will gain the requisite power
to raise your comrades from death.
 
-Lao
